, including location variables, our findings can\nbe applied globally.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Aug 2022 18:37:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Apr 2023 07:57:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-13"}
