h respect to a traditional trigger scintillator as well as an\nexcellent time resolution. Secondly, a fast LGAD plane has been proposed to\nprovide a time resolution of a few 10 ps, which is foreseen to drastically\nimprove the timing performance of the telescope. Time resolutions of below 70\nps have been determined in collaboration with the University of California,\nSanta Barbara.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Aug 2022 09:19:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-24"}
